<codeline><highlight class="normal">│<sp/><sp/><sp/>└──<sp/>YourShader.ixx</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">└──<sp/>...</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">src/ext/yourbackend/</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">├──<sp/>rendering/</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">│<sp/><sp/><sp/>├──<sp/>YourRenderingDevice.cpp</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">│<sp/><sp/><sp/>└──<sp/>...</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">└──<sp/>...</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>4.<sp/>Update<sp/>CMake</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Add<sp/>your<sp/>backend<sp/>to<sp/>the<sp/>build<sp/>system:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```cmake</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>In<sp/>src/ext/CMakeLists.txt</highlight></codeline>
