<codeline><highlight class="normal">```</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Design<sp/>Principles</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">1.<sp/>**Abstract<sp/>Interfaces**:<sp/>The<sp/>core<sp/>helios<sp/>framework<sp/>defines<sp/>interfaces,<sp/>not<sp/>implementations.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">2.<sp/>**Dependency<sp/>Injection**:<sp/>Applications<sp/>receive<sp/>concrete<sp/>implementations<sp/>via<sp/>factories.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">3.<sp/>**Modularity**:<sp/>Each<sp/>extension<sp/>is<sp/>an<sp/>independent<sp/>C++23<sp/>module.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">4.<sp/>**Interchangeability**:<sp/>Backends<sp/>can<sp/>be<sp/>swapped<sp/>without<sp/>changing<sp/>application<sp/>code<sp/>(only<sp/>the<sp/>factory<sp/>call).</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
